It’s true a picture says 1000 words but there’s so much that a picture doesn’t say.

I’ve learned over the years that it’s so easy to capture your best moments while displaying nothing about all the difficult times it took to get there.

This picture reminds me to stay grounded , appreciate life , appreciate the people apart of my life ; to show gratitude to every one , thing, and being. 

I’ve had so many tough moments that I had to dig deep, really find my purpose, and realize what I’m here to learn and take from this life that is never shown to the public.

However, I’m so grateful for all the highs AND lows that are shaping me to become the woman I am. 

No matter what you see looking from the outside in, know that everyone has bad days and nobody is perfect. 

Most importantly, choose to make today a great day 💕
